## 1. PROJECT OVERVIEW

**Name**: BioZackTeam (BZT) Fitness Platform  
**Purpose**: Fitness coaching platform with 3 user roles  
**Revenue Goal**: €10k/month by end 2026  
**Stack**: React 18 + TypeScript + Vite + Tailwind CSS + Firebase  

### User Roles
```
coach      → Full access. Manages clients, reviews check-ins, assigns workouts, posts content
coaching   → Paying coaching clients. Check-ins, assigned workouts, messages, community
community  → Free members. Browse programs, community feed, video library (locked videos hidden)
```

### What's Working (DO NOT TOUCH)
```
✅ Firebase Authentication (email/password)
✅ AuthContext.tsx — role detection, session management
✅ DataContext.tsx — all app state via localStorage
✅ LanguageContext.tsx — EN/AR bilingual + RTL
✅ Login.tsx — sign-in only (no self-registration)
✅ Dashboard.tsx — role-based dashboard router
✅ CheckIn.tsx — client weekly check-in form
✅ CoachReview.tsx — coach reviews client check-ins
✅ Clients.tsx — coach manages client list
✅ Messages.tsx — coach ↔ client messaging
✅ Community.tsx — community feed (posts, likes, comments)
✅ VideoLibrary.tsx — video library with lock/unlock
✅ Profile.tsx — user profile page
✅ All 7 training data files (264 workouts across 42 programs)
✅ restDayEngine.ts — rest day calculation (rewrite only, keep exports identical)
✅ AppRoutes.tsx — protected routes with role-based access
✅ Layout.tsx — sidebar navigation + background
✅ Firebase hosting, Firestore rules, Storage rules
```

